headline: Intercontinental Exchange Launches Reddit Signals and Sentiment Tool Providing Actionable Market Indicators for Investors
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, January 28, 2026--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced the launch of Reddit Signals and Sentiment, a suite of data and analytical tools that transforms millions of Reddit conversations into structured, actionable market signals for investors.
